{"tid":510053,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜5歲「綁馬尾」嫩照曝光","createTime":"2017-12-26T05:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:45:34.000Z","uid":34489,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c65f222304bfb7332dff8ba0661875fd7566125","tid":510053,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"記者蕭采薇／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓年度盛事《SBS歌謠大戰》25日在首爾高尺巨蛋盛大展開，陪伴歌迷度過聖誕節日，由IU和柳熙烈擔任主持人，包括EXO、防彈少年團、Wanna One、TWICE等歌手共襄盛舉。節目在回顧過往曾獲的「大賞」的藝人時，同步也放出現正活躍的偶像，在當年還是小孩的嫩照。而在2003年年份時，也曝光了當時5歲的子瑜嫩照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3012/d3012032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3012%2Fd3012032.jpg&h=08870a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SBS歌謠大戰曝光了子瑜5歲的照片。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3012/d3012051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3012%2Fd3012051.jpg&h=f512745c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜現在和過去幾乎不太有差別。（圖／翻攝自Youtube、SBS）"},{"pid":"9f72bf05b13b0018c1497333b2da10f99dd4e138","tid":510053,"uid":151774,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"普通料"},{"pid":"9398430b48f0794c2b15d5eb9ea9b5151d0849d8","tid":510053,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f72bf05b13b0018c1497333b2da10f99dd4e138","tid":510053,"uid":151774,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"普通料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dcbcbda22141893a8feb446d7d32ed1b488321","tid":510053,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T05:29:01.000Z","msg":"尋晚見到momo都有張8歲既😇"},{"pid":"665f2162952eeaba029e83416b76e08f4c902ccb","tid":510053,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59dcbcbda22141893a8feb446d7d32ed1b488321","t